data.description: DESIRABLE LOCATION IN PBG & PRICED TO SELL QUICKLY! Walk around the peaceful lake in this well-kept, pet-friendly neighborhood. Easy living, one level 3/2 patio villa, split plan, Metal roof 2016, A/C only a few years old.  Sold AS IS- price adjusted so buyer can make minor repairs & update. HOA is only $390 month and includes exterior insurance, roof, common areas, mgmt, Xfinity basic cable & internet. Up to 2 Pets allowed total weight = 50lbs, no commercial vehicles, no lease first 2 yrs of owning, 2 assigned parking spaces. Community: wide sidewalks w/pet stations, 2 pools, pickleball, tennis, racquet & basketball courts. GREAT LOCATION- drive to  beach, Roger Dean Stadium, shops, restaurants, near 3 Publix's &  medical centers
